Why am l not surprised?

588
00:42:19,537 --> 00:42:22,267
l'm glad you do not dismiss
a lowly waiter, Agent Kelly.

589
00:42:22,406 --> 00:42:23,634
l am Ming.

590
00:42:24,575 --> 00:42:26,042
Dr. Huang is here?

591
00:42:26,343 --> 00:42:28,038
