592
00:42:31,215 --> 00:42:32,910
So you knew Professor Wen?

593
00:42:33,651 --> 00:42:36,552
No, l didn't know him.
Chicago's a big place.

594
00:42:37,254 --> 00:42:38,983
And what did you know about him?

595
00:42:39,323 --> 00:42:41,018
He seemed very well liked.

596
00:42:42,159 --> 00:42:43,786
His wife was very nice.

597
00:42:46,497 --> 00:42:49,933
There was a big demonstration
on campus protesting his death.

598
00:42:50,067 --> 00:42:53,867
And this demonstration, what
was it trying to say?

599
00:42:54,038 --> 00:42:56,666
lt was trying to connect his
death to your government.

600
00:42:57,074 --> 00:42:59,235
Does that seem impossible to you?

601
