Well, l know about his affiliation
with the Bamboo Tigers Gang.

602
00:43:11,488 --> 00:43:13,888
You really must speak with
Dr. Huang.

603
00:43:58,268 --> 00:44:01,294
How does arresting me prevent a
Communist takeover?

604
00:44:04,775 --> 00:44:06,265
Where are you going with this?

605
00:44:08,078 --> 00:44:11,844
Why were you meeting with
Dr. Huang? Hm?

606
